{"tid":2189743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克鋼琴生產商因議長訪台 遭北京客戶取消訂單","createTime":"2020-09-05T06:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T06:09:17.000Z","uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3f69aa7fdf0fa7b576457509bbe75c012cb192","tid":2189743,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"捷克知名鋼琴製造商Petrof被北京客戶，以捷克參議院議長維斯特奇爾訪問台灣，影響中捷關係為由，臨時取消訂單。捷克新聞社引述Petrof總裁指出，該訂單總值530萬捷克克朗，折合大約183萬港元。取消訂單的北京客戶表示，中國政府正計劃對捷克製造的產品實施禁運，無法繳交罰款，唯有取消訂單。Petrof目前營業額大約35%來自中國，品牌憂慮，中捷關係惡化，會影響未來在中國的營商環境，亦不肯定公司員工能否順利取得簽證，參加下月舉行的上海國際樂器展覽會。維斯特奇爾訪台之行引起中方高度不滿，外長王毅日前警告，他將付出深重代價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-09-05 13:42:11 (1)"},{"pid":"362b2b5b9077c5dabca6004e608e35d18e57a43c","tid":2189743,"uid":224801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"等睇同歐盟反面"},{"pid":"814b23c6c5d721f02d540527610ba466ad888f7f","tid":2189743,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同埋身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"eb0e4fc2740dec43eeea530745d981f0d7d18aac","tid":2189743,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:09:17.000Z","msg":"咁做只會加快脫勾"}],"pinned":{"pid":"814b23c6c5d721f02d540527610ba466ad888f7f","tid":2189743,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dis